This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3673

Aldmeris is based on the oblivion theme for gedit.

Features:

- tango colors palette
- support GUI, 256 and 16 colors for terminal emulators
- option to use different terminal base colors in the colorscheme
- tpope's fugitive support: well recognizable colors for the output of :Gstatus, and for git objects.

Screenshot: https://github.com/veloce/vim-aldmeris/raw/master/screenshots/aldmeris.png

https://github.com/veloce/vim-aldmeris


